trans-unit.source: Defines an abstract base class for composable part definitions, which describe and enable the creation of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Definierar en abstrakt basklass för sammansättbara delen definitioner, som beskriver och skapa <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of a part that the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> describes.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en ny instans av en del som den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> beskrivs.

trans-unit.source: Derived types that override this method should return a new instance of a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object every time that the method is invoked and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Härledda typer som åsidosätter den här metoden ska returnera en ny instans av en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>objektet varje gång som metoden anropas och aldrig ska returnera `null`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the objects exported by the part defined by this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en samling <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"> </xref> objekt som beskriver exporterade den del som definierats av detta objekt <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Åsidosättningar av den här egenskapen ska aldrig returnera `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not provide exported objects, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Om den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>objekt som skapas av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>inte ange exporterade objekt, returneras en tom <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>samling i stället.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the exported objects provided by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects created by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En samling <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"> </xref> objekt som beskriver de exporterade objekten som tillhandahålls av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> objekt som skapas av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the imports required by the part defined by this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en samling <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"> </xref> objekt som beskriver import krävs av den del som definierats av detta <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Åsidosättningar av den här egenskapen ska aldrig returnera `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not have imports, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Om den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>objekt som skapas av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>inte har import, returneras en tom <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>samling i stället.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the imports required by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects created by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En samling <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"> </xref> objekt som beskriver import krävs av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> objekt som skapas av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the metadata for this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en samling av metadata för den här <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should return a read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object with a case-sensitive, non-linguistic comparer, such as <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>, and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Åsidosättningar av den här egenskapen ska returnera en skrivskyddad <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>objekt med en skiftlägeskänslig, icke-språkliga jämföraren som <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>, och aldrig ska returnera `null`.</xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A> </xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> does not contain metadata, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object instead.
trans-unit.target: Om den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>inte innehåller metadata, returneras en tom <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>objekt i stället.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the metadata for the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En samling som innehåller metadata för den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty, read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är en tom, skrivskyddad <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> objekt.
